Notes to developers:
   - Please keep track of all new key functionality in this file.  Make it
        a habit to edit this list as soon as you add a new key.
   - Only use <Shift> and <Ctrl> modifiers with ALPHABET KEYS.
   - Ctrl-C, Ctrl-H, Ctrl-I and Ctrl-M are reserved -- DO NOT USE THESE KEYS.
   - Ctrl keys are reserved to be used for entity specific functions.
     The mappings for these keys will depend on the entity class.
   - Do not put entity specific funtions on any keys except Ctrl keys.


*****************************************************************************
LOWER CASE ALPHABET:
*****************************************************************************

a:
   Entity accelerate
b:
c:
   Toggle clouds on/off.
   DVW = sendCloudPDUtest
d:
   Entity decelerate
e:
f:
   Toggle fog on/off.
   DVW = setHazeOn
g:
   Increase cloud level (both bottom and top levels).
h:
   Decrease cloud level (both bottom and top levels).
i:
   Entity switch input devices.
j:
   Increase cloud level (both bottom and top levels).
k:
   Decrease cloud level (both bottom and top levels).
l:
m:
   Toggle metric/english measurement systems.
n:
   Narrow field-of-view (FOV).
o:
   Toggle display of control measures.
p:
   TOGGLE_DVW_PRINT_SWITCH
q:
   Cycle munition specific field (for colored smoke).
r:
   Reset terrain and static databases (stop smoke, remove craters, revive
      destructable local entities.)
   DVW = cloudClean and deleteAllPlumes
s:
   Entity stop
t:
   Cycle time-of-day.
u:
   Half cloud thickneess.
v:
   Enable/Disable video missle.
w:
   Widen field-of-view (FOV).
x:
   Increase entity snapping range filter.
y:
   Double cloud thickness.
z:
   Decrease entity snapping range filter.


