   Increase HUD radar range.
[:
{:
]:
}:
\:
|:
;:
::
':
":
,:
<:
   Decrease amount of fog (increase near fog plane).
.:
>:
   Increase amount of fog (decrease near fog plane).
/:
?:
   Query information about current setup.  Information shown to shell window.


*****************************************************************************
FUNCTION KEYS:
*****************************************************************************

F1:
     Toggle display of Performer statitics.
     CTRL = Cycle statistics collection modes.
F2:
     Toggle HUD left text display on/off.
F3:
     Toggle HUD right text display on/off.
F4:
     Cycle HUD radar display modes.
     SHIFT - Toggle HUD radar all on/all off.
F5:
     Toggle texture.
F6:
     Toggle wireframe.
F7:
     Toggle antialias.
F8:
F9:
     Entity transport to position 1 (from file).
     SHIFT - Entity transport to position 5 (from file).
     CTRL - Entity transport to position 9 (from file).
     SHIFT,CTRL - Entity transport to position 13 (from file).
     When paused, above keys will save the current entity position and view
        as a new tranpsort position and will change the file at termination. 
F10:
     Entity transport to position 2 (from file).
     SHIFT - Entity transport to position 6 (from file).
     CTRL - Entity transport to position 10 (from file).
     SHIFT,CTRL - Entity transport to position 14 (from file).
     When paused, above keys will save the current entity position and view
        as a new tranpsort position and will change the file at termination.
F11:
     Entity transport to position 3 (from file).
     SHIFT - Entity transport to position 7 (from file).
     CTRL - Entity transport to position 11 (from file).
     SHIFT,CTRL - Entity transport to position 15 (from file).
     When paused, above keys will save the current entity position and view
        as a new tranpsort position and will change the file at termination.
F12:
     Entity transport to position 4 (from file).
     SHIFT - Entity transport to position 8 (from file).
     CTRL - Entity transport to position 12 (from file).
     SHIFT,CTRL - Entity transport to position 16 (from file).
     When paused, above keys will save the current entity position and view
        as a new tranpsort position and will change the file at termination.


*****************************************************************************
SPECIAL KEYS:
*****************************************************************************

Tab:
             Cycle HUD radar transparency.
Backspace:
             SHIFT = Entity reset state immediately to alive/healthy.
             CTRL = Entity toggle invulnerability.
Enter:
             SHIFT = Entity reset input control to resting state.
Insert:
             Entity set vertical/horizontal angles equal to gaze/weapon
             angles and then reset gaze/weapon angles to zero.
Delete:
             Entity reset gaze/weapon postion offset to zero.
Home:
             Entity fire primary weapon
End:
             Entity fire secondary weapon
PageUp:
             In bird's eye view: Entity increase viewing distance to self.
PageDown:
             In bird's eye view: Entity decrease viewing distance to self.
PrintScreen:
             Save the current graphics view to .rgb file.
Pause:
             Entity toggle movement - halt/restart position changes.
Space:
             Entity fire tertiary weapon
             DVW = SHIFT = createNewFlare


*****************************************************************************
ARROW KEYS:
*****************************************************************************

Left:
           Entity decrease horizontal angle (heading/roll).
Right:
           Entity increase horizontal angle (heading/roll).
Up:
           Entity increase vertical angle (pitch).
           SHIFT = Entity increase absolute Z (altitude).
Down:
           Entity decrease vertical angle (pitch).
           SHIFT = Entity decrease absolute Z (altitude).
Pad Left:
           Entity decrease horizontal gaze/weapon angle (heading/roll).
           CTRL = Bird's eye view = Rotate view to left around self.
Pad Right:
           Entity increase horizontal gaze/weapon angle (heading/roll).
           CTRL = Bird's eye view = Rotate view to right around self.
Pad Up:
           Entity increase vertical gaze/weapon angle (pitch).
           CTRL = Bird's eye view = Rotate view up around self.
Pad Down:
           Entity increase vertical gaze/weapon angle (pitch).
           CTRL = Bird's eye view = Rotate view down around self.

Pad 5:
           Entity reset gaze/weapon angles to zero.


